Package: disordR
Title: Tools for Charge–Hydropathy, Disorder Consensus, and pLDDT IDRs
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(first = "Hannah", last = "Cardenas",
           email = "hannah.cardenas03@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Small helpers for IDP analysis. Compute Uversky charge–hydropathy
    metrics and plots, combine outputs from disorder predictors into a consensus,
    and call putative IDRs from AlphaFold pLDDT with simple visualizations.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports: readr, dplyr, stringr, tibble, ggplot2
Suggests: bio3d
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/hannahcardenas4/disordR
BugReports: https://github.com/hannahcardenas4/disordR/issues
